comment: Squark-gluino production cross sections. The cross-section values reported here assume a 8-fold squark degeneracy (i. e. ~u, ~d, ~c, ~s mass degenerate). Provided by the authors of NNLL-fast (arXiv:1607.07741), including the combined scale and PDF+AlphaS uncertainties. The PDF set used for the calculations is NNLO PDF4LHC21 Hessian (LHAPDF ID 93300), and renormalization scale is set equal to factorization scale.
